/div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>To begin with, let me tell you a bit about my past article on the stock. I initiated <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/oakoff-investments/analysis?ticker=SMCI#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">my coverage</a> of <strong>Super Micro Computer</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>) stock in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4662482-super-micro-computer-stock-is-still-undervalued\">mid-January 2024</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1935446586/image_1935446586.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742164-super-micro-computer-smci-that-was-a-game-changer", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 01:20:46"}, {"id": "4742158", "title": "No, Rocket Lab Stock Does Not Defy Gravity (Technical Analysis)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman looking at friend jumping high up in sky\" data-id=\"1770285634\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1770285634/image_1770285634.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, 