36.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">TasfotoNL/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Readers of my latest articles know that I am bullish on British American Tobacco (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BTI\" title=\"British American Tobacco p.l.c.\">BTI</a></span>), as I have stated my reasons to be optimistic about the company in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4724567-british-american-tobacco-quality-at-a-huge-discount\">my first article here</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/577303436/image_577303436.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742156-british-american-tobacco-new-glo-hilo-looks-like-a-winner", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 01:09:12"}, {"id": "4742155", "title": "Devon Energy: 'When Will I Be Loved?'", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/180730079/image_180730079.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bride Throwing Bouquet For Guests To Catch\" data-id=\"180730079\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1295px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/18