ss=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Foot Locker retail store - burred shoppers walking by, Plymouth, UK\" data-id=\"1437842779\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Wirestock</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Foot Locker, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FL\" title=\"Foot Locker, Inc.\">FL</a></span>) released <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362456-foot-locker-non-gaap-eps-of-0_33-misses-0_07-revenue-of-1_96b-misses-40m\">Q3 2024 results</a>, disappointing the market by not meeting 3Q24 guidance and <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362463-earnings-snapshot-foot-locker-trims-fy-sales-profit-outlook-after-q3-miss\">lowering FY24 guidance</a>. The <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4362423-biggest-stock-movers-wednesday-crm-mrvl-and-more\">stock moved down</a> 10% the day after the release.</p> <p>Under the hood, there were many things to like</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1437842779/image_1437842779.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742154-foot-lockers-q3-not-that-bad-though-market-was-spooked-still-a-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 00:47:18"}, {"id": "4742152", "title": "Karat Packaging: Tariffs Can Hurt Earnings", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Szechuan beef Served with Rice as Take Out Food\" data-id=\"865655518\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">GMVozd/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The planned tariffs of the incoming U.S. administration spell trouble for the earnings of Karat Packaging Inc (NASDAQ: <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KRT\" title=\"Karat Packaging Inc.\">KRT</a></span>). The company doesn\u2019t have much pricing power, as evidenced by the drop in sales last year. Therefore, the tariffs will likely have a significant</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/865655518/image_865655518.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742152-karat-packaging-tariffs-can-hurt-earnings", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 00:44:49"}, {"id": "4742151", "title": "AT&T Investor Day: Doubling Down On The Right Things", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/965085346/image_965085346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AT&amp;T Mobility Wireless Retail Store. AT&amp;T now offers IPTV, VoIP, Cell Phones and DirecTV\" data-id=\"965085346\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/965085346/image_965085346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/965085346/image_965085346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/965085346/image_965085346.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/965085346/image_965085346.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/965085346/image_965085346.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/g